text: Everett is a city in the American state of Washington. It is the county seat of Snohomish County. As of 2020, 110,629 people live in Everett. The city is where Boeing builds many of its airplanes, like the Boeing 747 and Boeing 787. It is also where the United States Navy has a base called Naval Station Everett. == References == == Other websites == * City website Category:County seats in Washington (state)
